Remember every little thing.
Bixby helps you remember it all. Set up smart reminders to get notified when and where you need to. Reminders also work with specific apps, so you'll always remember to call someone back or send an important text.1






















Wach
Film








			Remember what you want.
			

			Go beyond your standard to-dos with reminders that include content. Whether it's an email, a webpage or even a video timestamp, reminders deliver exactly what you want.




				Remember what you want.
			

				Go beyond your standard to-dos with reminders that include content. Whether it's an email, a webpage or even a video timestamp, reminders deliver exactly what you want.































































Create reminders in a snap.
Bixby works seamlessly with your phone's apps and share menu, so you can talk, type or tap to create a reminder.










Voice commands
Use Bixby to create complex reminders just by speaking. So if you say, "Bixby, remind me to pick up milk and peanut butter when I get to the store," Bixby will create an itemized checklist and deliver it when you arrive.




Share Via
Reminder is now included in the same menu you use to share content with contacts and other apps.




Built into apps
Set reminders in apps like Phone and Messenger so you won't forget what you need or who you need it from.




Type reminders
Manually set reminders by typing them directly into the Reminder app.¹








































			Keep your reminders close.
			

			Accessible reminders make it easy to remember the little things.
			



				Keep your reminders close.
			

				Accessible reminders make it easy to remember the little things.
			
















Bixby Recommends
Check the reminders that are most relevant by swiping to Bixby and mark them complete. If a reminder has content attached, Bixby will take you directly to that app.











Widget
Store the Reminder widget on your home screen - it shows your upcoming reminders and takes you to them in the Reminder app.











Always On
The Always On display lets you see the most pressing reminders without touching your phone.











Edge Panel
Catch a glimpse at your reminders from any screen by swiping left from the right edge.1














Keep it organized.

From the things you need to do on your phone, like remember to watch a video, to things you need to do, like get milk, you can keep your important to-dos in one place.












