What you need, when you need it.

With Bixby, you'll get what you need at a glance, without having to open a single app. Whatever you're looking for is just a tap or swipe away.1











			See in a tap or swipe.


			Press the Bixby button to quickly find what you're looking for. You can also swipe your home screen to the right. In a single-tap you'll see upcoming appointments, today's photos, tomorrow's weather and more.
			



				See in a tap or swipe.


				Press the Bixby button to quickly find what you're looking for. You can also swipe your home screen to the right. In a single-tap you'll see upcoming appointments, today's photos, tomorrow's weather and more.
			









































Bixby knows what apps you need.
Bixby learns your routine to serve up the right content and information when you need it. By looking for patterns in your app usage by time and location, Bixby can predict what you might be looking for.









Morning workout
Workout every morning? Bixby knows your schedule. So every morning when you wake up to head to the gym, your alarm, weather, playlist, and Samsung Health are accessbile.




Lunch break
Catch up on the news over lunch? Every day you can see your calendar, read the news, and scroll Facebook with Bixby.




Nightly commute
Always take off from work at 6:30? Now you can order an Uber in a tap, and then easily find that Youtube video you've been waiting to watch all day.




Beach day
Head to the beach every Saturday? Bixby knows your weekend rituals too so Foursquare and your gallery will be handy when you need them.1








































			Do it from a single screen.


			Bixby goes beyond what a single app can do by using multiple functions across different apps in a single tap.1




				Do it from a single screen.


				Bixby goes beyond what a single app can do by using multiple functions across different apps in a single tap.1












Access just about everything.

Bixby keeps what's relevant just a swipe away to make it easier to do more, like looking at photos, calling your friends or texting your mom.1
 








Wach
Film











Use your apps in a new way.

Bixby also centralizes functionality from various apps. So you can order an Uber directly from a meeting on your calendar, and then check out each invited colleague's LinkedIn profile on the way there.1








Wach
Film











Available Apps.
Bixby works with a lot your favorite apps to help make everything you normally do a little bit easier.











